---
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-bg"></div>
  <div class="hero-content container">
    <p class="hero-en">BEYOND THE CHART</p>
    <h1 class="hero-title">海图之外</h1>
    <div class="gold-line" style="margin: 1rem auto;"></div>
    <p class="hero-tagline">他们驶入了海图上没有标记的海域。<br/>在那里，海水会抹去一切不完美的事物。</p>
    <div class="hero-actions">
      <a href={`${base}story/`} class="btn-primary">开始阅读</a>
      <a href={`${base}about/`} class="btn-secondary">了解更多</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 80vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .hero-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 80%, #0d2240 0%, var(--bg) 70%);
    z-index: 0;
  }
  .hero-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }
  .hero-en {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--gold-dim);
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .hero-title {
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-heading);
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
  }
  .hero-tagline {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    max-width: 500px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }
  .hero-actions {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  .btn-primary {
    padding: 0.7rem 2rem;
    background: var(--gold);
    color: var(--navy);
    font-weight: 600;
    border-radius: 4px;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }
  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: var(--gold-bright);
    color: var(--navy);
  }
  .btn-secondary {
    padding: 0.7rem 2rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--gold-dim);
    color: var(--gold);
    border-radius: 4px;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }
  .btn-secondary:hover {
    background: rgba(200, 164, 92, 0.1);
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero { min-height: 60vh; }
    .hero-title { font-size: 2.2rem; }
    .hero-tagline { font-size: 0.95rem; }
  }
</style>
